272
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:55,870
Seorang pertapa yang dilahirkan.

273
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,640
Berapa umur dia?

274
00:11:58,510 --> 00:11:59,970
Saya tidak tahu usia sebenar dia.

275
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:00,890
Walau bagaimanapun,

276
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:03,270
