298
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:38,000
Mereka memanggil mereka "Bakat Syurga."

299
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:38,550
Xin Mei ialah

300
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:40,730
Bakat Syurga Xin Xie Manor.

301
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:43,640
Dia tidak kelihatan

302
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,620
