451
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:31,540
Parit pecah, ladang ditenggelami air,

452
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:33,830
orang menjadi gelandangan.

453
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:36,690
Daerah Wei kami agak bertuah.

454
00:17:36,690 --> 00:17:38,170
Di bandar yang paling teruk dilanda,

455
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,350
